<p>8 basilei Dareiw cairein panta gnwsta estw tw kuriw hmwn tw basilei oti paragenomenoi eiV thn cwran thV IoudaiaV kai elqonteV eiV Ierousalhm thn polin katelabomen thV aicmalwsiaV touV presbuterouV twn Ioudaiwn en Ierousalhm th polei oikodomountaV oikon tw kuriw megan kainon dia liqwn xustwn polutelwn xulwn tiqemenwn en toiV toicoiV</p>
<p>9 kai ta erga ekeina epi spoudhV gignomena kai euodoumenon to ergon en taiV cersin autwn kai en pash doxh kai epimeleia sunteloumena</p>
