<p>24 ou to uyoV phcewn exhkonta platoV phcewn exhkonta dia domwn liqinwn xustwn triwn kai domou xulinou egcwriou kainou enoV kai to dapanhma doqhnai ek tou oikou Kurou tou basilewV</p>
