<p>3 kai euoda egineto ta iera erga profhteuontwn Aggaiou kai Zacariou twn profhtwn</p>
<p>4 kai sunetelesan tauta dia prostagmatoV tou kuriou qeou Israhl</p>
<p>5 kai meta thV gnwmhV Kurou kai Dareiou kai Artaxerxou basilewV Perswn sunetelesqh o oikoV o agioV ewV trithV kai eikadoV mhnoV Adar tou ektou etouV basilewV Dareiou</p>
<p>6 kai epoihsan oi uioi Israhl kai oi iereiV kai oi Leuitai kai oi loipoi oi ek thV aicmalwsiaV oi prosteqenteV akolouqwV toiV en th MwusewV biblw</p>
