<p>10 kai hgagosan oi uioi Israhl twn ek thV aicmalwsiaV to pasca en th tessareskaidekath tou prwtou mhnoV oti hgnisqhsan oi iereiV kai oi Leuitai ama</p>
<p>11 kai panteV oi uioi thV aicmalwsiaV ouc hgnisqhsan oti oi Leuitai ama panteV hgnisqhsan</p>
