<p>10 kai ta filanqrwpa egw krinaV prosetaxa touV boulomenouV ek tou eqnouV twn Ioudaiwn airetizontaV kai twn ierewn kai twn Leuitwn kai twn de en th hmetera basileia sumporeuesqai soi eiV Ierousalhm</p>
