<p>74 kai dia taV amartiaV hmwn kai twn paterwn hmwn paredoqhmen sun toiV adelfoiV hmwn kai sun toiV basileusin hmwn kai sun toiV iereusin hmwn toiV basileusin thV ghV eiV romfaian kai aicmalwsian kai pronomhn meta aiscunhV mecri thV shmeron hmeraV</p>
